    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>The action of a person or animal using their legs to go faster than a walk, specifically to go steadily by springing steps so that both or all feet leave the ground for an instant in each step. May be employed as a competitive sport.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
